data.name: IL0001Description
data.value: Reference types like classes cannot be used in kernels.

data.name: IL0001MessageFormat
data.value: Type '{0}' is a reference type. Reference types like classes cannot be used in kernels, except for arrays of value types.

data.name: IL0002Description
data.value: Arrays of reference types cannot be used in kernels.

data.name: IL0002MessageFormat
data.value: Type '{0}' is an array of type '{1}', which is a reference type. Arrays of reference types cannot be used in kernels.

data.name: IL0002Title
data.value: Array of reference types in kernel
